 Fuel Cycle is seeking a Chief Technology Officer (CTO) to support our mission to unleash the power of customer insights to legendary brands. As our CTO, you will report directly to the Chief Executive Officer (CEO) and will be responsible for identifying new capabilities to use technology to deliver cutting-edge products, providing technical leadership, and ensuring alignment between our technology and company strategy. Our ideal candidate has expertise that covers architecture, people management, data and analytics, artificial intelligence, machine learning, developer platforms, and software development. An exceptional candidate will pair their technological expertise with customer empathy to create mission-critical products our users love. 
